      <title>英美资源集团 (Anglo American) 铜年产量增长 24%</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/anglo-american-posts-24-rise-annual-copper-output-2024-02-08/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球矿业公司英美资源集团 (Anglo American) 周四公布，去年铜产量增长 24%，达到 826,000 吨，低于此前预测的 830,000-870,000 吨范围。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/anglo-american-posts-24-rise-annual-copper-output-2024-02-08/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 07:42:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
