      <title>日产第三季度利润增长 6%，未达预期</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/nissan-posts-6-q3-profit-rise-missing-estimates-2024-02-08/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本日产汽车周四公布，12 月份季度营业利润增长 6.4%，低于预期，并表示将维持年度预期，因为利润更高的产品组合抵消了较低的全年汽车销量预测。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/nissan-posts-6-q3-profit-rise-missing-estimates-2024-02-08/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 07:36:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
