      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/british-american-tobacco-forecasts-low-revenue-growth-2024-2024-02-08/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英美烟草公司周四预测，有机收入增长将为低个位数，并补充称，预计美国经济将缓慢复苏。]]></description>
